high_descs: Turn around to face the coffee machine on the counter.
Take the mug from the coffee machine.
Turn to the right and then left towards the sink.
Lift the mug up to the microwave above the sink. Place the mug inside the microwave and shut the door. After the microwave turns off take the mug out and shut the door.
Look back down at the sink and turn left to go back to the coffee machine.
Put the mug back on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Warm up a mug in the microwave to place it in the coffee machine

high_descs: Turn around 180 degrees and face the coffee machine.
Pick up the coffee mug from the machine.
Turn 90 degrees to the right and turn 90 degrees to the left when you reach the sink.
Open the microwave, put the mug inside, close the microwave, heat up the mug, remove the mug from the microwave, and close the microwave door.
Turn 90 degrees to the left and walk back towards the coffee machine.
Place the mug back under the spout and wait for coffee to be made.
anns.task_desc: Heat up some water in order to make coffee in a coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the coffee maker on the counter.
Pick the cup up from under the coffee maker.
Go right and stand in front of the sink under the microwave.
Put the cup in the microwave, turn the microwave on and then take the cup out.
Go left and stand at the counter in front of the coffee maker.
Put the cup under the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated cup under the coffee maker.
